title: Hillary Clinton arrives in India for a private visit
text:
Hillary Clinton arrives in India for a private visit Monday, March 12, 2018 - 00:51 
Former U.S. Secretary of State Hillary Clinton is visiting India for a private visit, and on Monday toured Jahaz Mahal, an acient fort. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
